{"tid":1007608,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日提醒你：深水埗新春熟食墟開幕","createTime":"2019-02-04T01:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T02:32:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"509188766da3a6916dea51ea3d39b991220bb008","tid":1007608,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T01:36:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190204/20606136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190204%2F20606136&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToBIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=5a4920a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190204%2F20606136&h=04dc4425\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190204/20606136</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年02月04日 <br />\n<br />\n今日提醒你：深水埗新春熟食墟開幕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190204/large/a0305a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190204%2Flarge%2Fa0305a.gif&h=90846105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n若不想逛傳統年宵市場，可到深水埗參加由關綜聯及多個地區團體舉辦的「新春『豚』年熟食墟」，有數十款街頭風味小食讓大家一飽口福。熟食墟大部份攤檔不提供即棄餐具，市民謹記自備餐具，為環保出一分力。<br />\n時間︰下午4時至午夜（4日）、下午4時至晚上11時（5及6日）<br />\n地點︰深水埗保安道遊樂場<br />\n網址︰ <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/63......92741051499/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F63......92741051499%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToBIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=b710c56c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/63......92741051499/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n年宵市場通宵掃平貨<br />\n<br />\n年三十晚吃團年飯後，當然要逛年宵市場感受節日氣氛。無論你想到全港最大的維園年宵市場，抑或到鄰近的年宵市場，都要切記︰「越夜越抵！」年宵市場會在大年初一清晨才結束，港鐵今晚亦一如以往提供通宵服務，各位不用擔心夜歸無車喇！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各區年宵市場地址： <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_....../lnyf2019/index_notice.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fehd.gov.hk%2Ftc_......%2Flnyf2019%2Findex_notice.html&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToBIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=1eca26f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fehd.gov.hk/tc_....../lnyf2019/index_notice.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n送狗迎豬　爭上頭炷香<br />\n<br />\n年三十晚另一重點節目，當然是到黃大仙祠爭上頭炷香。有意上頭炷香的市民可在今晚9時輪候，屆時祠內會實施單向人流管制，並不設跪拜、求籤及供品供奉，首批信眾將會在11時上香。嗇色園黃大仙祠通宵開放至大年初一下午6時正。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n內地逾800城市禁燃放<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n林正財撐放寬海外醫生　 倡設免試名單　先認可英澳愛爾蘭醫學院"},{"pid":"d492ebc2163c93d0f0bc002ce0e3e7c7f94d9d77","tid":1007608,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T01:45:16.000Z","msg":"自備餐具<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5591446bfad129aab60472ea2c4d91d426b8b35e","tid":1007608,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T02:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}